Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Within the Stone Wilderness, a mysterious Monster suddenly appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's a follower of the one who destroyed Atlantis years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Kris... Ironheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You two are the souls of warriors who fought against this threat alongside the Duel Monsters in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swear to you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I will fight with everything I've got to protect those close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Varon Engages!\N The Mysterious Armor Deck"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally reached the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow this railroad track, we should be able to meet up with Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell them both about this as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Yugi's going to be alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he's gone back to his usual self!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,198...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,199...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't move an inch~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}jerk{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's freakin' low! Catching me when my guard was down like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaddup! Win's a win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up an' pick up Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me take a quick break~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya sure it's okay to sit around like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna meet up with Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a move on, Honda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey- No, wait! Isn't that a little {\i1}too{\i0} fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta pace yourself properly! Pace yourself, ya moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as we'll\N tolerate your disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disobedience?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be clear on this. I never once agreed to Duel by anyone's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only fight the way I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes Pegasus as well as Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your {\i1}tongue{\i0}, Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, you weren't able to beat Jounouchi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a {\i1}break{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy didn't get in the way, I {\i1}would've{\i0} beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're still saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do what I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz! Even if it's {\i1}you{\i0}, I won't let anyone get in the way of my Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her do as she pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, her fate rests in the hands of our God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, sweety!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a hot bike you ridin' there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatd'ya say to comin'\N to play around with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was'sat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to {\i1}get lost{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do with that little computer image a' yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! That's not a hologram!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take care of Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your turn to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your sake, I'll beat Jounouchi to a bloody pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! For "my sake"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep your ridiculous jokes to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason behind our actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Reasons"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean those {\i1}eyes{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said yourself. You seek victory in order to never allow yourself to suffer the despair of defeat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that wasn't all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you were searching for something beyond mere victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like an exceptionally serious addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're manipulated by your own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something... beyond winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the walking dead in search of blood, you wander aimlessly for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you manage to win, your desires aren't fulfilled in the least bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only seek a new victory beyond the victory you already felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bullshit are you on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take for you to realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to shoulder this burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you achieve victory, you're becoming nothing but an overflowing vessel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi and the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They too have their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes Rafael and Amelda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of us has our own "container".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live on if I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to appease my "vessel of victory"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that, Mai, is {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your sake, I'll continue winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it Jounouchi or the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if you wish it so, I'll even defeat Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You have to defeat me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the same as I was back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be better off not thinking you can win so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the professor holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sound asleep in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I figured, he hasn't recovered from the shock of this whole thing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But my grandpa wanted us to set off ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of Doma's men!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otogi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two took Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole Yugi's soul, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what if we did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Becky! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't belittle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not look like it, but I'm the U.S. Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat this guy and win back Yugi's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? {\i1}Are{\i0} you now, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The U.S. Champion...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca Hopkins...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you underestimate me, you're in for some pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mature kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you wanna knock some sense into this kiddy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, I'm gonna show you a sample of my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky! Let me fight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With me tagging along, we'll be that much more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing. I'll take you both on at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky! Watch out for The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Psychic Armor Head in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He put a Monster with 0 Attack Points in Attack Position?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psychic Armor Head?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've heard of that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of powers does it have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play a Magic Card from my hand! Summon Dice activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pay 1000 of my Life to roll a die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the die rolls a one or a two, I'll be able to call an additional Summon outside of a Normal Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it lands a three or a four, I can Special Summon a Monster from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if it hits a five or a six...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a six!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tribute in order to Summon a High-Level Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, God Orgoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Sapphire Dragon in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then place a card face-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be able to attack next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Effect of Psychic Armor Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for drawing a card this turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can add one Armor Monster from my deck to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I sacrifice Psychic Armor Head to Summon Double Cross Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following, I set a card in reverse and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's he up to? He Summoned another Monster with 0 Attack Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Monster can't attack on the turn it's Summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it's attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the opposing Monster is destroyed by its Effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the opposing player takes half the destroyed Monsters' Attack Points as damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after engaging in battle, this card is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were to strike with God Orgoth, half of his Attack Power, 1250, would be deducted from my Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But next turn, he won't have a Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play two cards on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take care of the rest, Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Orgoth! Attack Double Cross Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Blade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance, Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Sapphire Dragon and Summon Emerald Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emerald Dragon, Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet Armor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card allows me to Special Summon one Armor Monster from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be Summoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Cross Armor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope of Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster enters my Cemetery as a result of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I toss my entire hand away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and increase that Monster's Attack Strength by 800 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can Special Summon it to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick-Play Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of Diamond Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card activates only when a Dragon-Type Monster is Special Summoned from the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:16:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing it, I can Special Summon one Diamond Head Dragon from the deck of the controller in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this well, Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Head Dragon's Attack Points are equal to the Attack Power of the sacrificed Monster, plus an additional 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think? Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've had more than enough fun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done playing games with the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psychic Armor Head has another Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is in the Graveyard, you can Special Summon it in Attack Mode during your Standby Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai, I'm gonna show you the passionate fire of my strength in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna use a card related to that Barrier of Orichalcos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not be conceited now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be needing the Barrier of Orichalcos against the likes of {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Gravitation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell {\i1}is{\i0} that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The armor attached itself directly to the player's body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this card is destroyed in battle, all cards on the field are destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the players receive damage equal to the Attack Points of their destroyed Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurd! If you did that, even you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna {\i1}test{\i0} me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... ENDS IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,USELESS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"THE END OF" CRUSHER!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Jounouchi a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him, "You're next."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making me carry Ryuzaki for 5,000 steps...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't my fault ya can't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Honda, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that? An aurora?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aurora? I remember last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is something about to start...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guided by time, my God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having absorbed powerful souls, it has begun to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't believe Yugi's lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just means he was not the man I thought he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's become a loser dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aurora?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! It's really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would an aurora occur all the way out here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are about to experience a little turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For your safety, please be seated and fasten your seatbelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:22:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to meet up with Jounouchi and Honda, whom we were separated from...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and I head back the way we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} heads to Florida in order to find the proof he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Doma makes another unavoidable move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda takes Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} on in a revenge match aboard a flying plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time's in midair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Revenging Amelda - The Great Airborne Duel"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
